parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
often when the brake pedal is depressed
the vehicle surges forward
the engine revs up
and the vehicle may continue to accelerate even when the gear is shifted into neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle does not stop or slows down unexpectedly
the vehicle accelerates when the brake pedal is depressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The interference of the floor mat with the accelerator pedal can lead to unintended acceleration, loss of control, accidents, and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The floor mat becomes stuck under the accelerator pedal
causing the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly
the driver has to release the floor mat while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering shaft can cause the loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the steering wheel shakes violently
the steering wheel detaches
the vehicle loses steering control
the steering shaft fractures
the lower bearing detaches from the steering column.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist can cause the loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power steering assist fails to operate as needed
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle loses steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering column shaft pulls apart
the steering column shaft fractures
the steering wheel detaches.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag light stays on
airbag fails to deploy
seat belt sensor fails to function
seat belt fails to lock.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accelerator pedal sticking can cause the vehicle to lunge forward, leading to accidents and potential injuries.
symptoms: Accelerator pedal becomes stuck
vehicle lunges forward
airbags fail to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt and Airbag Sensor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt and airbag sensors can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Seat belt sensor fails to function
seat belt fails to lock
airbag light stays on.
